I have always been passionate about *customer obsession* and *passion for invention*, and I envision myself contributing my talent to the furthering of AWS's goal of being Earth's most customer-centric and secure cloud. I would love to discuss my interest in this position with your team and can be reached at #ph or #eml. Thank you for your time and consideration, I look forward to connecting!

